# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:38
translate spanish hwb_s20_fe975720:

    # "The engine dies. I can still hear the power buzzing before it surges down, leaving us with the ambiance of the settling motorhome."
    "El motor se apaga. Todavía puedo oír el zumbido de la energía antes de que se apague, dejándonos con la atmósfera de la casa rodante estabilizándose."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:42
translate spanish hwb_s20_055d73c0:

    # Amber "We’re here."
    Amber "Приехали."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:46
translate spanish hwb_s20_cf6ab2b5:

    # Marina "Not a lot of cars here, huh?"
    Marina "Не особо тут много машин, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:50
translate spanish hwb_s20_6c691828:

    # Amber "Guess the rest of the world just hasn’t caught up yet."
    Amber "Видимо, пока не весь мир знает, что здесь спрятано сокровище."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:52
translate spanish hwb_s20_eb7ff0ce:

    # "That won’t last for long. Any day now, people will figure out it’s here and an army of would-be treasure hunters will be swarming this place, drooling at the chance to find gold."
    "Eso no durará mucho. En cualquier momento, la gente se dará cuenta de que está aquí y un ejército de buscadores de tesoros potenciales invadirá este lugar, babeando ante la oportunidad de encontrar oro."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:54
translate spanish hwb_s20_08721c86:

    # "The last of the gold."
    "El último del oro."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s20_a6ea5dbf:

    # "There's a fluttering in my chest, and I tighten my grip on the wheel."
    "Siento un aleteo en el pecho y aprieto el volante."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s20_a93d8d5e:

    # "It’s the end of our adventure."
    "Es el final de nuestra aventura."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s20_a96d7fbc:

    # Marina "I bet our names have spread across the land and struck fear into the hearts of our rivals, giving them no other choice but to call it quits!"
    Marina "Я думаю, что молва о нас разошлась по всей Земле, вызывая трепет и страх в сердцах соперников, и они предпочли сдаться!"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s20_2558da78:

    # Amber "Yeah. Or maybe someone already came through and found the treasure."
    Amber "Ага. Или кто-то уже пришел и нашел его."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s20_36d8f90d:

    # Marina "Wh-What? Don’t say something scary like that."
    Marina "Ч-что? Не говори такие ужасные вещи."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s20_6468e319:

    # "Still wrapped around the wheel, my clammy hands start shaking."
    "Aún aferradas al volante, mis manos húmedas empiezan a temblar."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s20_c104625b:

    # "Marina takes notice, looking over with sympathetic eyes."
    "Marina lo nota y me mira con ojos compasivos."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s20_32d7002e:

    # Marina "Hey."
    Marina "Эй."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s20_cd7dd212:

    # "She takes her hand and gently places it on top of mine, giving it a reassuring squeeze. I let both fall into my lap."
    "Toma su mano y la coloca suavemente sobre la mía, dándome un apretón reconfortante. Dejo que ambas caigan sobre mi regazo."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s20_509807b1:

    # "She’s warm."
    "Ella está cálida."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s20_ddc384a6:

    # Marina "We’re doing this together, okay?"
    Marina "Мы сделаем это вместе, хорошо?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s20_d7bbfdb5:

    # "The flutters tickle the inside of my chest until I can’t help smiling."
    "Los aleteos me cosquillean el pecho hasta que no puedo evitar sonreír."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s20_b9c1f238:

    # Amber "Right. Let’s do it."
    Amber "Да. Давай сделаем это."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:100
translate spanish hwb_s20_0a73024d:

    # "Regretfully, I force out a nod and pull my hand out from Marina’s."
    "Con pesar, fuerzo un asentimiento y retiro mi mano de la de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s20_1024071b:

    # "It feels wrong. Like throwing away a precious gift."
    "Se siente mal. Como tirar un regalo preciado."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:104
translate spanish hwb_s20_20ce37c4:

    # "Reaching into the console, I retrieve the journal, for what may be the last time."
    "Alcanzando la consola, recupero el diario, quizás por última vez."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s20_7a1a60c6:

    # "It’s well loved. A bent spine, wrinkled pages, and folded corners on the flimsy paper cover."
    "Está muy querido. Un lomo doblado, páginas arrugadas y esquinas dobladas en la cubierta de papel endeble."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s20_027f6bc4:

    # "Looking back, it’s been getting roughed up since the moment we got it. Ever since that weird station attendant Marina have it for free way back at the traveler’s store."
    "Mirando hacia atrás, ha estado maltratado desde el momento en que lo conseguimos. Desde que ese extraño empleado de la estación se lo regaló a Marina en la tienda de viajeros."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:114
translate spanish hwb_s20_40ed20d2:

    # "Hard to believe this cheap thing was the road map to something so valuable."
    "Es difícil creer que esta cosa barata fuera el mapa hacia algo tan valioso."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s20_4fabf4b6:

    # "Taking a deep breath, I skim over the final entry."
    "Tomando un respiro profundo, hojeo la última entrada."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s20_7c5a0031:

    # Amber "Windstone Arch."
    Amber "Арка Виндстоун."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s20_0d6b5fa8:

    # "It’s probably the vaguest entry so far, but I can feel it. It has to be there."
    "Probablemente sea la entrada más vaga hasta ahora, pero lo siento. Tiene que estar ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s20_a0cec1af:

    # "I slap the journal shut and lay it to rest in the center console, right next to all the cassette tapes."
    "Cierro el diario de golpe y lo dejo reposar en la consola central, justo al lado de todos los casetes."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s20_38b89ef5:

    # "Marina and I look at each other, now sharing the same piercing determination."
    "Marina y yo nos miramos, compartiendo ahora la misma determinación penetrante."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s20_bed2c428:

    # Amber "Alright, let’s get this show on the road."
    Amber "Ладно, погнали."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s20_cbbeb9f8:

    # "Because of the lack of crowds, getting around is a lot easier than usual, allowing us to take in the scenery for once instead of slogging through zombified hoards."
    "Debido a la falta de multitudes, moverse es mucho más fácil de lo habitual, permitiéndonos disfrutar del paisaje por una vez en lugar de arrastrarnos entre hordas zombificadas."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:187
translate spanish hwb_s20_bb2c509e:

    # "Even though there’s not many people around, it somehow feels {i}fuller{/i} here."
    "Aunque no hay mucha gente alrededor, de alguna manera se siente {i}más lleno{/i} aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s20_2e768d3b:

    # "Everywhere we walk, we’re surrounded by layered dunes and sandstones, towering over us, striped with faded reds and calico browns."
    "Dondequiera que caminamos, estamos rodeadas de dunas y areniscas en capas, que se elevan sobre nosotras, rayadas con rojos desvaídos y marrones calicó."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s20_2a07a2c2:

    # "Somehow, we do eventually manage to find the Windstone Arch."
    "De alguna manera, al final logramos encontrar el Arco de Piedra de Viento."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:194
translate spanish hwb_s20_f6d3a06f:

    # "Unlike the arches back in Utah, it isn’t big and majestic. It’s not a giant upside down horseshoe that lords over us as we look on in awe."
    "A diferencia de los arcos en Utah, no es grande ni majestuoso. No es una herradura gigante invertida que nos domina mientras lo contemplamos con asombro."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:196
translate spanish hwb_s20_04e8031e:

    # "It’s not even an arch, as much as it is a cave, really. Just a jagged, overgrown rock with a few crevices big enough for a person to enter."
    "Ni siquiera es un arco, sino más bien una cueva, en realidad. Solo una roca dentada y cubierta de maleza con algunas grietas lo suficientemente grandes para que una persona entre."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s20_c35d9e74:

    # "Still, despite this—despite the fact that it doesn’t compare to the size or grandeur of everything else we’ve seen together so far, and despite that it hardly took us any time at all to find it—it’s still imposing."
    "Aun así, a pesar de esto—a pesar de que no se compara con el tamaño o la grandeza de todo lo demás que hemos visto juntas hasta ahora, y a pesar de que apenas nos tomó tiempo encontrarlo—sigue siendo imponente."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s20_4bf0fe34:

    # "The longer I stare at it the bigger it gets, like it’s judging us. It isn’t calling into question our abilities or even if we can find it."
    "Cuanto más lo miro, más grande se vuelve, como si nos estuviera juzgando. No está cuestionando nuestras habilidades ni siquiera si podemos encontrarlo."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s20_031d2e67:

    # "It’s gauging us to see if we’re ready."
    "Está evaluándonos para ver si estamos listas."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s20_7b81f614:

    # "Are we?"
    "¿Lo estamos?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s20_abb00a0b:

    # "I look over to Marina. A small bulge forms in her throat before she swallows it back down."
    "Miro hacia Marina. Un pequeño bulto se forma en su garganta antes de que lo trague."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s20_1ef83274:

    # "Is she?"
    "¿Lo está ella?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s20_7580c1da:

    # "I return my gaze to the Arch, asking the same questions over and over in my head."
    "Devuelvo la mirada al Arco, haciéndome las mismas preguntas una y otra vez en mi cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:219
translate spanish hwb_s20_4c631aaa:

    # "Am I?"
    "¿Lo estoy yo?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s20_e198a3ef:

    # "Finally, we look to each other. Marina readies the metal detector strapped to her back and gives me a nod, which I return."
    "Finalmente, nos miramos la una a la otra. Marina prepara el detector de metales que lleva atado a la espalda y me asiente, y yo le devuelvo el gesto."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s20_7c5efd18:

    # "Even if we aren’t ready, even if this is the worst mistake of my life, this is something both of us have to do."
    "Incluso si no estamos listas, incluso si este es el peor error de mi vida, esto es algo que ambas tenemos que hacer."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s20_eec0aade:

    # "Our steps in sync, we march over the rocks and desert shrubs before crouching into the cavern."
    "Con pasos sincronizados, avanzamos sobre las rocas y los arbustos del desierto antes de agacharnos para entrar en la caverna."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s20_05bed716:

    # "Sunlight squeezes into the cave, dyeing the rock columns neon-red."
    "La luz del sol se cuela en la cueva, tiñendo las columnas de roca de un rojo neón."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:246
translate spanish hwb_s20_a92aeabe:

    # "Marina begins scanning with the metal detector, listening intently for a beep."
    "Marina comienza a escanear con el detector de metales, escuchando atentamente un pitido."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s20_9527780f:

    # "The narrow space forces us to huddle together as we heave our way through the arch, repeatedly brushing against each other."
    "El espacio estrecho nos obliga a apiñarnos mientras avanzamos con dificultad a través del arco, rozándonos repetidamente."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s20_e785321f:

    # "At first, it’s accidental, but I find myself craving it more."
    "Al principio, es accidental, pero me encuentro deseándolo más."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s20_3349c1d5:

    # "To get closer."
    "Para acercarme más."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s20_8a387110:

    # "To feel her."
    "Para sentirla."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s20_2d8de8b6:

    # "To watch as her hair absorbs the brilliant glow of the cave."
    "Para ver cómo su cabello absorbe el brillo radiante de la cueva."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s20_fac31763:

    # "I’m deprived of all of that though, as her metal detector vibrates in her hand, making a low rumble."
    "Pero me veo privada de todo eso, cuando su detector de metales vibra en su mano, emitiendo un rumor grave."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:266
translate spanish hwb_s20_c5433470:

    # "She takes off the headphones and points to the wall."
    "Se quita los auriculares y señala la pared."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s20_d1a0b7c7:

    # Marina "There."
    Marina "Вот там."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s20_7a90a2f3:

    # "I avert my gaze and move past her, taking a knee as I slip the bag off my shoulder and pull out a mandrill pickaxe."
    "Desvío la mirada y paso a su lado, arrodillándome mientras deslizo la mochila de mi hombro y saco un pico de mandril."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s20_995921a0:

    # "Careful not to hit her, I start chiseling away at the rock."
    "Con cuidado de no golpearla, empiezo a cincelar la roca."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s20_93cc77f9:

    # "Soon, the crack in the wall grows and small pebbles and gravel starts flying off."
    "Pronto, la grieta en la pared crece y pequeñas piedras y gravilla comienzan a desprenderse."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:292
translate spanish hwb_s20_46cf475b:

    # "I reposition myself and block Marina from getting hit by any of it."
    "Me recoloco y bloqueo a Marina para que no reciba ningún golpe."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s20_eea38e6d:

    # "The small portion of the wall crumbles away and after a few more strikes, reveals a hollow space, just big enough to squeeze your hand into."
    "La pequeña porción de la pared se desmorona y, tras unos cuantos golpes más, revela un espacio hueco, justo lo suficientemente grande para meter la mano."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s20_507ea000:

    # "This is gonna suck if some creepy thing’s gone and made its home in there."
    "Esto va a apestar si alguna cosa espeluznante ha hecho su hogar ahí dentro."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s20_1e67e60e:

    # "Shuddering, I reach into the space and feel something square and wooden. With some budging, it comes free and easily slides out."
    "Estremeciéndome, meto la mano en el espacio y siento algo cuadrado y de madera. Con un poco de esfuerzo, se suelta y se desliza fácilmente hacia afuera."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s20_faa49a75:

    # "A box."
    "Una caja."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s20_d7e21c56:

    # "Its familiarity is expected, but it doesn’t stop my heart from leaping any less, nor Marina’s, who squeaks out a gasp."
    "Su familiaridad es esperada, pero no impide que mi corazón dé un brinco, ni el de Marina, que deja escapar un jadeo."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s20_373fa4e6:

    # Amber "Ready?"
    Amber "Готова?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s20_83ac2061:

    # "This time, she barely nods, unsure of what to say, but like ripping off a bandage, I swing the lid open before she can give any real answer."
    "Esta vez, ella apenas asiente, sin saber qué decir, pero como si arrancara una curita, abro la tapa de golpe antes de que pueda dar una respuesta real."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s20_c5088209:

    # "Nuggets. A pile of them. Filled from top to bottom, all misshapen and morphed."
    "Pepitas. Un montón de ellas. Llenas de arriba a abajo, todas deformes y retorcidas."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s20_2dbcdee1:

    # "The sight isn’t anything new, but this time it feels different. It’s like for the first time, the reality has finally sunk in and everything up until now has been a haze."
    "La vista no es nada nuevo, pero esta vez se siente diferente. Es como si por primera vez la realidad finalmente hubiera calado y todo hasta ahora hubiera sido una neblina."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s20_1d9f982b:

    # "We both just stare at it. An entire universe of thoughts race through my mind, yet it all comes up blank."
    "Ambas nos quedamos mirándolo. Todo un universo de pensamientos cruza por mi mente, pero todo queda en blanco."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s20_06aebe8a:

    # Amber "What now?"
    Amber "Что теперь?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s20_b78588e4:

    # "It’s directed more towards myself than Marina, but it’s the first thing I manage to spit out, and ultimately the most important."
    "Está dirigido más hacia mí misma que hacia Marina, pero es lo primero que logro soltar, y al final, lo más importante."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s20_748d732c:

    # "Marina doesn’t answer at first, instead just tilting her head, trying to process the question. But finally, she gives a simple smile."
    "Marina no responde al principio, solo inclina la cabeza, tratando de procesar la pregunta. Pero finalmente, esboza una simple sonrisa."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s20_e07ed01a:

    # Marina "I saw a sign for a trail on the way over here. Why don’t we go hiking?"
    Marina "Я видела знак, указывающий, что здесь есть пешеходная тропа. Почему бы нам не прогуляться?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s20_b967cb89:

    # "‘Hiking?’"
    "—¿Caminata?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s20_9dd0c698:

    # "I freeze for a second, then laugh under my breath."
    "Me quedo congelada un segundo, luego río en voz baja."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s20_c84ccb57:

    # "The more I think about the simplicity behind her words, the more I laugh, until I border on sounding like a hysterical madman."
    "Cuanto más pienso en la simplicidad detrás de sus palabras, más me río, hasta que rozo sonar como una histérica loca."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s20_a368fd26:

    # Amber "Hiking… For real?"
    Amber "Прогуляться… Правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s20_1ae3ee4d:

    # "I keep laughing, struggling to keep it together, even after I start having trouble breathing."
    "Sigo riendo, luchando por mantener la compostura, incluso después de que empiezo a tener problemas para respirar."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s20_77a7633f:

    # "Poor Marina isn’t in on the joke though, and within a matter of seconds her face goes from confusion, to concern, then pouting."
    "La pobre Marina no está al tanto de la broma, y en cuestión de segundos su rostro pasa de confusión a preocupación, y luego a un puchero."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s20_a81c66f2:

    # Marina "I dunno why you’re laughing. I was being serious, y’know…"
    Marina "Не знаю, чего ты смеешься. Я вообще-то серьезно, знаешь ли…"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s20_d1723f53:

    # "Settling down, I wipe a fake tear from my eye, an occasional chuckle still managing to break through."
    "Calmándome, me limpio una lágrima falsa del ojo, mientras una risita ocasional aún logra escapar."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s20_d1bb68a3:

    # Amber "No, no, I know you were."
    Amber "Нет, нет. Я знаю, что ты серьезно."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s20_a45f9caf:

    # Marina "Then what’s so funny?"
    Marina "Тогда что смешного?"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s20_776aec28:

    # Amber "Nothing. Just…"
    Amber "Ничего. Просто…"

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s20_09ee300e:

    # "I finally regain complete composure and smile at her."
    "Finalmente recupero la compostura por completo y le sonrío."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:366
translate spanish hwb_s20_20b96c4e:

    # Amber "Yeah, sure. Let’s go hiking. That sounds nice."
    Amber "Да, конечно, пойдем прогуляемся. Звучит заманчиво."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s20_e5051f51:

    # "Looking back, it’s been getting roughed up since the moment we got it. Ever since that weird station attendant let Marina have it for free way back at the traveler’s store."
    "Mirando hacia atrás, ha estado maltratada desde el momento en que la conseguimos. Desde que ese extraño empleado de la estación se la dejó llevar gratis a Marina en la tienda de viajeros."

# game/script/hwb_s20.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s20_05313ec1:

    # "Because of the lack of crowds, getting around is a lot easier than usual, allowing us to take in the scenery for once instead of slogging through zombified hordes."
